                    </p>
                    <div class="about-features">
                        <div class="feature">
                            <i class="fas fa-heart"></i>
                            <span>Small Town Service</span>
                        </div>
                        <div class="feature">
                            <i class="fas fa-shield-alt"></i>
                            <span>Licensed & Insured</span>
                        </div>
                        <div class="feature">
                            <i class="fas fa-user-check"></i>
                            <span>Background Checked Staff</span>
                        </div>
                        <div class="feature">
                            <i class="fas fa-handshake"></i>
                            <span>Community Trusted</span>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="about-stats">
                    <div class="stat">
                        <h3>35+</h3>
                        <p>Belleview Homes</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="stat">
                        <h3>4</h3>
                        <p>Years Serving Community</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="stat">
                        <h3>5</h3>
                        <p>Star Reviews</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Comprehensive Belleview Local Content -->
    <section style="background: white; padding: 4rem 0;">
        <div class="container">
            <div style="max-width: 900px; margin: 0 auto; line-height: 1.7; color: #555;">
                <h2 style="color: #2f5047; margin-bottom: 2rem; text-align: center;">Belleview Community & Local Living Expertise</h2>
                
                <h3 style="color: #2f5047; margin: 2rem 0 1rem;">Understanding Belleview's Growing Community Character</h3>
                <p style="margin-bottom: 1.5rem;">
                    Belleview's <strong>steady growth from 4,492 residents in 2010 to 5,982 in 2025</strong> reflects a thriving community that attracts families, young professionals, and retirees seeking small-town charm with modern amenities. This 1.8% annual growth rate creates a dynamic environment where established neighborhoods welcome new residents, creating unique cleaning needs that bridge traditional home maintenance with contemporary living standards.
                </p>
                
                <p style="margin-bottom: 1.5rem;">
                    The community's <strong>diverse demographic mix</strong> includes 59.62% family households and 40.38% non-family units, creating a varied residential landscape where our cleaning services adapt to everything from busy family homes with children to professional couples and retiree households. This diversity requires flexible service options and deep understanding of different lifestyle needs within Belleview's close-knit community structure.
                </p>

                <p style="margin-bottom: 1.5rem;">
                    <strong>Marion County School District's above-average ratings</strong> make Belleview particularly attractive to families with school-age children, creating specific cleaning challenges around homework areas, play spaces, and the increased activity that comes with active family living. Our services support busy parents who value both cleanliness and the time savings that professional cleaning provides for family activities and community involvement.
                </p>

                <h3 style="color: #2f5047; margin: 2rem 0 1rem;">Belleview Housing Characteristics & Cleaning Considerations</h3>
                <p style="margin-bottom: 1.5rem;">
                    Belleview's <strong>median home value of $214,300</strong> reflects an affordable housing market where residents take pride in maintaining their properties as significant investments. The fact that 53.36% of properties are purchased with mortgages and average monthly housing costs reach $912 indicates a community of homeowners who understand the importance of proper maintenance and cleaning to protect their property values over time.
                </p>

                <p style="margin-bottom: 1.5rem;">
                    The community's <strong>suburban rural mix atmosphere</strong> means many Belleview homes feature larger lots, established landscaping, and outdoor living spaces that require specialized attention. Florida's climate combined with more spacious properties creates unique cleaning challenges around screen enclosures, pool areas, and outdoor furniture that must withstand year-round use while maintaining the attractive appearance that characterizes Belleview neighborhoods.
                </p>

                <p style="margin-bottom: 1.5rem;">
                    Many Belleview homes reflect <strong>traditional Florida architecture</strong> with features like tile roofs, stucco exteriors, and covered porches that create distinctive cleaning needs. Our team understands the proper care of these materials and architectural features, ensuring that cleaning methods enhance rather than damage the characteristic elements that give Belleview homes their charm and value.
                </p>

                <h3 style="color: #2f5047; margin: 2rem 0 1rem;">Demographics & Lifestyle Service Adaptations</h3>
                <p style="margin-bottom: 1.5rem;">
                    Belleview's <strong>median age of 44</strong> creates a community where active adults balance career demands, family responsibilities, and community involvement. This demographic sweet spot means our cleaning services often support busy professionals who participate actively in local events, school activities, and community organizations while maintaining homes that reflect their pride in Belleview's reputation and character.
                </p>

                <p style="margin-bottom: 1.5rem;">
                    The community's <strong>84.09% white-collar workforce</strong> with an average commute time of 28.8 minutes indicates residents who value their time and understand the benefits of professional services that allow them to focus on careers and family rather than household maintenance. Our scheduling flexibility accommodates these working professionals while ensuring homes remain clean and welcoming for family life and entertaining.
                </p>

                <p style="margin-bottom: 1.5rem;">
                    <strong>High home ownership rates</strong> in Belleview mean residents are invested in their properties and community long-term, creating demand for consistent, reliable cleaning services that support property maintenance goals. Our relationship-based approach aligns with Belleview's small-town values, where service providers become trusted community partners rather than anonymous vendors.
                </p>

                <h3 style="color: #2f5047; margin: 2rem 0 1rem;">Transportation Corridor Benefits & Environmental Factors</h3>
                <p style="margin-bottom: 1.5rem;">
                    Belleview's position along <strong>major transportation routes including U.S. Routes 27, 301, and 441</strong> provides excellent accessibility while also creating specific environmental challenges for home maintenance. Heavy traffic corridors generate additional dust and debris that can affect homes, particularly those closer to these major thoroughfares, requiring adjusted cleaning approaches and schedules to maintain pristine conditions.
                </p>

                <p style="margin-bottom: 1.5rem;">
                    The <strong>10-mile proximity to Ocala</strong> means many Belleview residents commute to larger employment centers while returning to the peace and quiet of small-town living each evening. This lifestyle pattern creates specific cleaning needs around entryways, mudrooms, and areas where work clothes and daily accumulation of city dust require regular attention to maintain the clean, comfortable atmosphere that makes home a retreat.
                </p>

                <p style="margin-bottom: 1.5rem;">
                    Central Florida's <strong>climate patterns affect Belleview homes</strong> throughout the year, with seasonal variations in pollen, humidity, and storm activity that require adaptive cleaning approaches. Our local expertise helps Belleview residents manage these environmental factors while maintaining homes that remain comfortable and welcoming regardless of Florida's weather challenges.
                </p>

                <h3 style="color: #2f5047; margin: 2rem 0 1rem;">Economic Considerations & Value-Based Service</h3>
                <p style="margin-bottom: 1.5rem;">
                    Belleview's <strong>median household income of $48,252</strong> reflects a community of working families who make careful decisions about service investments. Our competitive pricing and flexible service options ensure that professional cleaning remains accessible to Belleview residents who want quality results without compromising their household budgets. We understand that in smaller communities, value and reliability matter more than flashy marketing.
                </p>

                <p style="margin-bottom: 1.5rem;">
                    The presence of <strong>11.03% entrepreneurs</strong> in Belleview's workforce creates opportunities to support local business owners who understand the challenges of running a service-based business. Many of our Belleview clients are fellow small business owners who appreciate the attention to detail and customer service focus that comes with working with a locally owned cleaning company that shares their community values.
                </p>

                <h3 style="color: #2f5047; margin: 2rem 0 1rem;">Seasonal Patterns Specific to Belleview</h3>
                
                <div style="background: #f8fafa; padding: 2rem; border-radius: 15px; margin: 2rem 0;">
                    <h4 style="color: #ff8057; margin-bottom: 1rem;"><i class="fas fa-sun" style="margin-right: 0.5rem;"></i>Spring & Summer Community Activity (March - September)</h4>
                    <p style="margin-bottom: 1rem;">
                        <strong>Increased community engagement</strong> during warmer months brings Belleview residents together for outdoor events, school activities, and neighborhood gatherings. These social seasons create higher demand for home preparation cleaning, post-event cleanup, and maintaining homes that frequently welcome neighbors and friends. Our flexible scheduling accommodates these community-focused lifestyles.
                    </p>
                    <p style="margin-bottom: 1rem;">
                        <strong>Summer vacation patterns</strong> for families with school-age children mean homes experience different usage patterns, from deep cleaning before family trips to catch-up cleaning after vacation returns. Our seasonal service adjustments help Belleview families manage these transitions while maintaining clean, organized homes throughout the busy summer months.
                    </p>
                </div>

                <div style="background: #f8fafa; padding: 2rem; border-radius: 15px; margin: 2rem 0;">
                    <h4 style="color: #ff8057; margin-bottom: 1rem;"><i class="fas fa-leaf" style="margin-right: 0.5rem;"></i>Fall & Winter Residential Focus (October - February)</h4>
                    <p style="margin-bottom: 1rem;">
                        <strong>Back-to-school season</strong> creates intensive cleaning needs as families establish routines, organize study areas, and prepare homes for the structured schedules that come with the academic year. Our services help busy Belleview parents maintain clean, organized environments that support family success and well-being during these demanding months.
                    </p>
                    <p>
                        <strong>Holiday entertaining</strong> takes on special significance in Belleview's close-knit community, where neighbors frequently gather for celebrations and seasonal events. Our pre-holiday cleaning services ensure that Belleview homes are ready to welcome family and friends, while post-holiday cleanup helps residents transition smoothly back to regular routines.
                    </p>
                </div>

                <h3 style="color: #2f5047; margin: 2rem 0 1rem;">Community Values & Service Philosophy</h3>
                <p style="margin-bottom: 1.5rem;">
                    Belleview's motto <strong>"City with Small Town Charm"</strong> perfectly captures the community spirit that guides our service approach. In Belleview, neighbors know each other by name, local businesses are valued, and service providers are expected to contribute positively to the community fabric. Our commitment goes beyond cleaning to supporting the values and relationships that make Belleview such a desirable place to call home.
                </p>

                <p style="margin-bottom: 1.5rem;">
                    The community's <strong>conservative-leaning population</strong> often values traditional approaches to business relationships - honesty, reliability, and quality workmanship delivered with personal attention and fair pricing. Our old-fashioned commitment to customer service and community involvement aligns perfectly with these expectations, creating lasting relationships built on trust and consistent performance.
                </p>

                <h3 style="color: #2f5047; margin: 2rem 0 1rem;">Property Investment & Community Standards</h3>
                <p style="margin-bottom: 1.5rem;">
                    <strong>Above-average car ownership</strong> (2 cars per household) and high homeownership rates indicate Belleview residents are invested in their community and properties for the long term. This stability creates demand for consistent, reliable cleaning services that support property maintenance goals while respecting the community relationships and reputation that matter in smaller towns.
                </p>

                <p style="margin-bottom: 1.5rem;">
                    Belleview's <strong>growing population and stable housing market</strong> create opportunities for residents to build equity and community connections over time. Our cleaning services support these goals by helping maintain properties in excellent condition while freeing up time for residents to participate in the community activities and relationships that make Belleview such a special place to live.
                </p>

                <div style="background: #e8f5f2; padding: 2rem; border-radius: 15px; margin: 2rem 0;">
                    <h4 style="color: #2f5047; margin-bottom: 1rem; text-align: center;">Why Belleview Residents Choose Palma Cleaning</h4>
                    <div style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr)); gap: 1.5rem; margin-top: 1.5rem;">
                        <div style="text-align: center;">
                            <i class="fas fa-heart" style="font-size: 2rem; color: #ff8057; margin-bottom: 0.5rem;"></i>
                            <h5 style="color: #2f5047; margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">Small Town Values</h5>
                            <p style="font-size: 0.9rem;">Personal service and community commitment that reflects Belleview's friendly, neighbor-helping-neighbor atmosphere</p>
                        </div>
                        <div style="text-align: center;">
                            <i class="fas fa-handshake" style="font-size: 2rem; color: #ff8057; margin-bottom: 0.5rem;"></i>
                            <h5 style="color: #2f5047; margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">Trusted Local Service</h5>
                            <p style="font-size: 0.9rem;">4+ years building relationships with Belleview families and understanding unique community needs</p>
                        </div>
                        <div style="text-align: center;">
                            <i class="fas fa-dollar-sign" style="font-size: 2rem; color: #ff8057; margin-bottom: 0.5rem;"></i>
                            <h5 style="color: #2f5047; margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">Fair Value Pricing</h5>
                            <p style="font-size: 0.9rem;">Competitive rates that respect working families' budgets while delivering professional quality results</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Services Section -->
    <section id="services" class="services">
        <div class="container">
            <h2 class="section-title">Belleview Cleaning Services</h2>
            <div class="services-grid">
                <div class="service-card">
